PN,31501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FA once-a-day pill helped to almost
OL,8,Fdouble survival time for patients with
OL,9,Fan aggressive and advanced form of
OL,10,Fpancreatic cancer when compared to
OL,11,Fchemotherapy, a trial has found.
OL,13,FThe new drug, daraxonrasib, also
OL,14,Fcaused fewer side effects, with
OL,15,Fexperts describing it as "landscape-
OL,16,Fchanging" for people with the disease.
OL,26,@wD@ZOUxD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
