FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FDaraxonrasib works by locking onto the
OL,8,Fmutated KRAS gene, which is found in
OL,9,Fmore than nine in 10 pancreatic
OL,10,Ftumours and signals cancer cells to
OL,11,Fgrow.
OL,13,FBy shutting this off, the drug
OL,14,Fprevents tumours from spreading, the
OL,15,Fresearch showed.
OL,17,FPancreatic Cancer UK said new
OL,18,Ftreatments targeting the gene variant
OL,19,Fare "some of the most exciting
OL,20,Fdevelopments" in a very long time, and
OL,21,Fcalled for clinical trials in the UK.
OL,26,@{D@EOU|D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
