PN,31503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FThe trial, which was presented at the
OL,8,FAmerican Society of Clinical Oncology
OL,9,F(Asco) annual meeting in Chicago,
OL,10,Fincluded 500 patients in North
OL,11,FAmerica, Europe, and Asia with
OL,12,Fadvanced pancreatic cancer which had
OL,13,Fspread to other organs.
OL,15,FThey had previously received treatment
OL,16,Fand were still able to carry out most
OL,17,Fof their daily activities.
OL,19,FRoughly 248 patients were given
OL,20,Fdaraxonrasib and 252 were given
OL,21,Fchemotherapy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FMost had tumours with specific
OL,8,Fmutations of the KRAS gene.
OL,10,FDuring a follow-up period, the median
OL,11,Fsurvival time for patients on
OL,12,Fdaraxonrasib was 13.2 months compared
OL,13,Fto 6.6 months among those on
OL,14,Fchemotherapy.
OL,16,FThe median time spent without the
OL,17,Fdisease progressing was 7.3 months in
OL,18,Fthe daraxonrasib group and 7.2 months
OL,19,Fin the chemotherapy group.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
