FL,316,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FDaraxonrasib also caused fewer serious
OL,8,Fside effects, according to the study.
OL,9,FThe new drug triggered severe side
OL,10,Feffects in 43.6% of patients, compared
OL,11,Fto 57.5% of patients on chemotherapy.
OL,13,FJust 1.2% of people in the
OL,14,Fdaraxonrasib group stopped treatment
OL,15,Fbecause of side effects compared to
OL,16,F11.2% of the chemotherapy group.
