PN,31506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FRachna Shroff, chief of the division
OL,8,Fof haematology/oncology at the
OL,9,FUniversity of Arizona Cancer Centre
OL,10,Fand an Asco expert in gastrointestinal
OL,11,Fcancers, said the drug was showing
OL,12,F"unprecedented survival and efficacy
OL,13,Fin second-line treatment with an
OL,14,Fexpected safety profile".
OL,16,F"The RAS revolution is here, and this
OL,17,Fstudy is proof of principle that
OL,18,Ftargeting KRAS in pancreatic cancer is
OL,19,Ffeasible and effective."
OL,26,@{D@XO]
