PN,31507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,FReacting to the findings, Anna Jewell,
OL,8,Fdirector of services, research and
OL,9,Finnovation at Pancreatic Cancer UK,
OL,10,Fsaid: "These new treatments targeting
OL,11,FKRAS mutations are some of the most
OL,12,Fexciting developments we have seen in
OL,13,Fpancreatic cancer for a very long time.
OL,15,F"KRAS mutations are found in over 90%
OL,16,Fof all pancreatic tumours and are
OL,17,Fresponsible for driving the rapid
OL,18,Fgrowth of this devastating disease.
OL,26,@rD@GOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
