PN,31508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"Crucially, these results suggest that
OL,8,Fdaraxonrasib is able to keep the
OL,9,Fcancer under control for longer."
OL,11,FThere are around 11,500 cases of
OL,12,Fpancreatic cancer diagnosed in the UK
OL,13,Feach year and around 10,200 deaths.
OL,15,FMs Jewell said: "Tragically, half of
OL,16,Fall people with pancreatic cancer die
OL,17,Fwithin just three months of their
OL,18,Fdiagnosis.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@QOU
