PN,31509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F315A1780333563
OL,3,CNew pill helps double survival time
OL,4,Cfor people with advanced pancreatic
OL,5,Ccancer
OL,7,F"More time with those we love most is
OL,8,Ftruly priceless. We must do everything
OL,9,Fpossible to ensure the most promising
OL,10,Fnew treatments are available here in
OL,11,Fthe UK."
